quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,146,"∆Āen …ďe Men Rokki Defere nden immorde e anndu…óu…ďe Alyahuuda e Annasaara en,hi…ďe nganndi wayleede Qibla on taw…óo ko gootel e maandeeji Annabaaku Muhammadu (yo O his) ka ma…ď…ďe,wano …ďe nganndiri …ďi…ó…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďe faaytnaŇčtaako …ďe.∆äum ha…óaali fedde goo e ma…ď…ďe hino suu…óa goonga ar…óo e mab…ďe,haasidaagol immorde e pittaali ma…ď…ďe, hi…ďe wa…óa …óum e hoore hi…ďe nganndi ko nde goonga."
  2,147,"Ko …óum …óoo woni goonga kan, wata laatodu -an Nulaa…óo- e …ďen sikkitii…ďe sellugol …óum."
  2,148,"Ena woodani kala mofte, baŇčŇče mo …ďe fewtata e mu'n, foti non ko ko memetee walla miijitee; wano luutondiral mofte ka huccitirde ma…ď…ďe e kon ko Allah Shar'inani …ďe, …óuu…óal yiilor…óe ma…ď…ďe lorrataa so tawii ko yamaruree Allah e shari'a Makko, adondiree -onon gom…óim…ďe- e huuwugol mo∆ī∆īereeji …ói yamira-…óon, Allah moo…ďitiroyay on kala nokku mo laatoroyton √Īalnde darngal; ngam O yo…ďita on golle mo'on. Pellet, Allah ko hattan…óo e dow kala huunde, O RoŇčkataa moo…ďtude on yo…ďa on."
  2,149,"Nokku kala mo yaltir-…óaa e kala ka laati-…óaa -an annabiijo-e jokku…ďe ma,faala…óaa juulude,fewtir baŇčŇče Juulirde Hormorde nden,sabu …óum ko goonga wahyinaa…óo ummoraade Joomi maa. Allah Wonaali Welsindii…óo e kon ko gollo-ton,ko woni,Himo ∆īellitii e …óum,O yo…ďoyay on …óum."
  2,150,"Nokku kala mo yaltir-…óaa-an Annabiijo-faala…óaa juulude,fewtir baŇčŇče Juulirde Hormaande nden.Nokku kala mo ngon…óon-onon gom…óim…ďe- fewtiniree geece mon …óen baŇčŇče mayru so on faalaamaa juulude;fii wata wonan yim…ďe …ďen hujja mo …ďe hujjinorta e dow mo'on-so wanaa …ďen too√Īu…ďe e ma…ď…ďe,…ďen …óon heddoday e geddi mu'un,…ďe hujjinora e mo'on ko …ďe yi…ói e hujjaaji,wata non on hulu…ďe,hulee Joomi mo'on tan, golliron yamirooje Makko wo…ó…óito-…óon ha…óaa…ói Makko.Pellet,Allah Shar'inirii fewtugol Kaaba on ngam Timminirgol neemaaji Makko ∆äin e mo'on fii Ko O seerndi on e denndaangal mofte,e fii no O Fewnira on ka …ďuri teddude e Qibla yim…ďe."
  2,151,"Ko wano non Men Neeminiri e mo'on neema goo; tawde Men Nulii e mo'on Nulaa…óo jeyaa…óo e mo'on, himo janngana on Aayeeje Amen, o la…ď…ďinira on kon ko o yamirta on immorde e …ďure e mo∆ī∆īere, e ko o ha…óata on e mu'um immorde e ellaaji e a√Īinii…ói, himo janngina on Al Qura'aanaare nden e Sunna on, o janngina on kon ko on anndaano e fiyakuuji diine e dunyaaru mo'on."
  2,152,"JaŇčtoree Lam …ďer…óe mo'on e ter…óe mo'on; Mi Annditira on MaŇčtugol on Reena on, njo…ďdi ndin ko e ndeer golle …óen woni. Jaarnee Lam e neemaaji Am …ói Mi Neemini e mo'on, wata on yeddira huutorgol …ói ka harmi."
  2,153,"Ko onon yo gom…óim…ďe, wallitoree mu√Ī√Īaare e juulde, tuma rewoton Lam jebbilano-…óon yamiroore Am. Pellet, Allah hino wonndi e mu√Ī√Īii…ďe …ďen, O Walliray-…ďe hawrindineede e sawaaba."